DTSTAMP:20260713T104504Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260626
SUMMARY:Deadline: Prairie Ronde Artist Residency: Summer/Fall 2026 (Michiga
 n)
DESCRIPTION:Prairie Ronde Artist Residency at The Mill at Vicksburg\, a sel
 f-directed residency open to artists across disciplines including film\, v
 ideo and new media. ELIGIBILITY: artists of any discipline\; open worldwid
